{"word":"G2173 - εὔχρηστος - eúchrēstos - yoo'-khrays-tos - Profitable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὔχρηστος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eúchrēstos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo'-khrays-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Profitable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பிரயோஜனமுள்ள, உபயோகமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"easy to make use of, useful"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and <a href=\"#/G5543 - χρηστός - chrēstós - khrase-tos'/5543\">G5543</a>; <i>easily used</i>, that is, <i>useful:</i> - profitable, meet for use.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}